        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Silvano veterano ex b<expan><ex>en</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciario</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tribun</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>domo Hemesa vexit <note>sic</note> annis LX Aurelia <lb n="3"/>Hilara coniuxs <note>sic</note> et <expan><abbr>Aureli</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Salvianus et Silvanus e&amp;lt;t=I&amp;gt; <lb n="5"/><surplus>et</surplus> Silvina <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> carissimi <lb n="6"/>et conheredes be<lb break="no" n="7"/>ne merenti et digno <lb n="8"/>posuerunt 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten; gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein Grab. Das Inschriftfeld wird von zwei geflügelten Genien flankiert. RIU: Z. 2: vixit.</p>
            </div>
